{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7e9bba9bb6","title":"“肃反是党中央搞错了”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4e0f61602a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"be5c925d21","name":"林墨荫"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"141756cb84","type":"title","text":"“肃反是党中央搞错了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"4748569601","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院林墨荫","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"423f117cf1","type":"subtitle","text":"（林墨荫：北京地质学院教授）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"c4bccdd417","type":"paragraph","text":"「一九五五年中国肃反扩大化了，党中央不能现在揭发承认，再过一个历史时代就可以提出来。因为现在是执政党。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"03fad1349c","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反是党中央搞错了，尤其在知识分子中更不应该搞。伤害了很多人的良心。」","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"253eae62f5","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反是党中央学习斯大林的错误，党中央搞错了，百分之五为反革命是估计错误，肃反在中国扩大化了。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"3f29a90d66","type":"paragraph","text":"「我院肃反搞的很糟，斗争面太广，市委有工作通报，批评了我院党委，且是第一号。」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"766c030d76","type":"paragraph","text":"「我院采取这种方式的肃反工作，成绩是主要的，我表示怀疑，不管用机械的统计方法也好，用辩证法也好都无法解决量与质的问题。我们要求党委通过肃反斗争的总结，教育我们分析事物的方法。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"9b0ba53b7c","type":"paragraph","text":"「肃反是农村方式。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"5af434b1f6","type":"paragraph","text":"「采取这种方式的肃反工作，成绩是主要的，我表示怀疑。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"},{"id":"da89f45af4","type":"paragraph","text":"「我不应该拿到群众会上来斗，因为别人对我不了解，了解我的人就不会把我当反革命。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6"}],"page":{"id":"6f39bf702a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7e9bba9bb6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}